item.title: Where i can find Item Codes?
item.dc:creator: @mr_luigi_77 mr luigi 77
item.description:
@mr_luigi_77 wrote:

Here’s an idea. Difficulty: -1/10 Needed: Nothing but a computer and knowledge of spelling.

  1. Go to google.com
  2. Type the following without the quotes: “Ezzarlscape client download”
  3. When it is finished downloading, extract it using Winrar.
  4. Extract it to the desktop.
  5. Double-click the folder that says: Ezzarlscape client v1.1
  6. Scroll down to the bottom, and double-click runserver, or run, or run.bat
  7. Wait for the client to load.
  8. Go to the top and left-click tools.
  9. Left-click Item IDS
  10. Congratulations. There’s your item IDS.
